title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Nov 3 2022

description:
Crime Blotter: Hillary lies, Sunny Hostin of The View calls white women "roaches" and the NYPD arrests rapist for 19th time. Hung Cao, refugee from Vietnam, veteran and GOP candidate in Virginia's 10th congressional district, joins Clay and Buck. Ohio Senate Candidate JD Vance gives C&B an update on his race.
